title: American_Top_40_Year_End_Countdowns
description:
I had the following request from a RocketMan Fan. "Do you have the Year-End Countdowns? I would especially like to have the 1979 Year-End Countdown."

Well, I have the Top 50 of 1979, the Top 40 of 1973 & 1977, and the Top 100 of 1974, 1976, 1983, 1984, 1985, and 1986. I haven't been through them to check for quality or do any editing. I plan to do that later in the year.

I also have the Top 100 hits of 1978 and 1980 ready to go. I was waiting for the end of the year but Mom always said, "Give the people what they want," so I will torrent those a few minutes after I get done here.

So here they are, just as I found them, all the year-end countdown shows that I have stashed away. I will give them a proper re-issue when the time comes.

RocketMan999
